text.content: I'ma be that nail in your coffin  Sayin' that I soften  I was duckin' down to reload  So you can save your petty explanations  I don't have the patience    Before you even say it I know  You let your pride and your ego  Talk slick to me no  That is not the way I get down  And look at how you lose your composure  Now let me show ya exactly how the breaking point sound    I wanna see you choke on your lies  Swallow up your greed  Suffer all alone in your misery  Choke on your lies  Swallow up your greed  Suffer all alone in your misery    What is it you want me to tell ya?
